desc.html: A scan of original, unused and now defunct Tasmanian Government Railways tickets, used on special trains to the Royal Hobart Show in the late 1970s. As there are no logos, and the design, issue and creation of these tickets have not been used or produced in over 30 years, I have scanned these under the pretences that they are fair use.

wiki.Credit: Scanned from original railway tickets, using Epson V370. Edited in PhotoShop.
